Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.44,0:22:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}兩舷原速前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.58,0:22:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}向150度方向前進
